 targets. In contrast,\nconsiderably more, 10-100%, of the flux can be attributed to DM when a\ncontracted Navarro-Frenk-White profile is assumed. This demonstrates how\nsensitive DM contributions to gamma-ray emissions are to the possibility of\ncored profiles in galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Jul 2017 09:56:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Sep 2017 14:25:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 19 Sep 2017 10:38:49 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 20 Sep 2017 09:13:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-17"}
