miconductor. This\n\"one-dimension-like\" few-layer Te, together with other geometrically similar\nlayered materials, may promote the emergence of a new family of layered\nmaterials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Jul 2017 14:37:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Sep 2017 11:42:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 9 Nov 2017 05:54:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 25 Dec 2017 09:12:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-07"}
